main_body:
Annex I to Regulation (EC) No 690/2008 is amended as follows:
(1) in the second column of points 4, 5 and 7 to 10 of heading (a), after the word ‘Greece’ the words ‘(until 31 March 2011)’ are replaced by ‘(until 31 March 2014)’;
(2) in the second column of point 2 of heading (b), after the word ‘Spain’ the words ‘(except the autonomous community of Castilla y León),’ are added;
(3) heading (d) is amended as follows:
(a) in the second column of point 3, after the word ‘Greece’ the words ‘(except the Prefecture of Argolida),’ are added;
(b) point 4 is replaced by the following:
‘4. Grapevine flavescence dorée MLO
